'''ADI 3510''' (April 29, 2008), is a landmark [[Supreme Court of Brazil|Brazil Supreme Court]] case. The minister relator [[Carlos Ayres Britto]] voted in favor of embryonic stem cell research (Biosecurity Law).<ref>[http://www.stf.jus.br/portal/cms/verNoticiaDetalhe.asp?idConteudo=204615 Abortion of Anencephalics in Brazil {{pt icon}}]</ref>
